{"tid":2416045,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【商業熱話】Tesla購入比特幣現帳面賺約47億，或已超過過去十年的公司利潤","createTime":"2021-02-20T17:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T15:30:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"50e286f78ec260ff19319e0d45c70eabab422918","tid":2416045,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rEwIiJnp91.v8A6tKMobcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ZrfINtwCF2ATLGN5ZPesNg--~B/aD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/business_digest_949/2656845b811eb6e6f1cd5491a375502b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrEwIiJnp91.v8A6tKMobcw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZrfINtwCF2ATLGN5ZPesNg--~B%2FaD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbusiness_digest_949%2F2656845b811eb6e6f1cd5491a375502b&h=1f3e556f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比特幣升勢似未見頂，該虛擬貨幣企上5萬美元。電動車大廠Tesla早前宣布在1月購入價值15億美元的比特幣，據媒體估算，不到一個月Tesla帳面上已賺6至11億美元（約47至86億港元），或已超過過去十年的公司利潤。<br />\n<br />\n媒體估算，Tesla在1月購入價值15億美元的比特幣，當時該虛擬貨幣價格在29,333美元到37,020美元之間，則大概可買到40,518至51,136枚比特幣。若以目前比特幣價格51,000美元計算，Tesla可以賺到6億至11億。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，Tesla在2020年才實現虧轉盈，全年盈利7.21 億美元，但在2019年公司全年虧損8.62 億美元。換句話，Tesla這10幾年來仍未完全實現盈利，而在這不到一個月中Tesla帳面上已賺6至11億美元。<br />\n<br />\nTesla行政總裁馬斯克日前在Twitter上評論到，Tesla行動不直接反映其意見，持有部分比特幣「只是不像現金那麼愚蠢的保持流動性方式」，指自己只有Tesla一家上市公司股份。他並表示：「我不是投資者，是工程師。」"},{"pid":"479fc4468e8b40982516c5dd9cf0cbbdcdf1bb95","tid":2416045,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"MicroStrategy  (MSTR) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa6ce